The original app had exceptional UI/UX — do not simplify or cut corners on design
Every screen must support RTL layout (Arabic is default)
Guest mode is supported — Supabase login is optional, sync only when logged in
The streak system tracks daily consecutive review days
The "Mem Science" screen (accessible from Home) explains the neuroscience behind the app — include it